@page "/about"
@page "/founder"

<div class="page-stack">
    <PageHero Kicker="About"
              Title="JPV-OS is built for operational excellence."
              Description="JPV-OS is a venture infrastructure platform that routes access, orchestrates resources, and enables structured execution across a full ecosystem of innovations, partnerships, and opportunities."
              Image="@AssetPaths.JayPVenturesLlc.Hero"
              ImageAlt="JPV-OS founder and operational vision" />

    <section class="content-section">
        <SectionHeader Kicker="The Founder"
                       Title="Jay PVentures: Infrastructure architect."
                       Description="JPV-OS and the broader JPV ecosystem were built by Jay PVentures as a response to operational complexity. The vision is simple: create infrastructure that routes people into the right environment, orchestrates their work, and enables them to build what comes next." />
        <div class="grid-3">
            <GlassCard Eyebrow="Philosophy" Title="Operational clarity" Description="Systems should be clear about what they do, who they serve, and how to access them. Complexity should be in the work, not the routing." />
            <GlassCard Eyebrow="Approach" Title="Infrastructure first" Description="Great infrastructure doesn't disappear. It orchestrates, routes, validates, and enables people to build at their best. That's what JPV-OS does." />
            <GlassCard Eyebrow="Practice" Title="Structured execution" Description="Every project, venture, and partnership routes through defined pathways. Governance, routing, and operational integrity keep everything aligned." />
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
        <SectionHeader Kicker="The Ecosystem"
                       Title="Built as a unified platform."
                       Description="JPV-OS is the orchestration layer that connects ventures, partnerships, infrastructure, and access into one operational surface. Everything routes through init, the application interface that keeps the ecosystem visible and legible." />
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="text-card">
                <h3>JPV-OS: The foundation</h3>
                <p>JPV-OS is the core infrastructure platform that manages routing, governance, orchestration, and operational integrity for the entire ecosystem.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-card">
                <h3>init: The application interface</h3>
                <p>init is where people enter the ecosystem. It shows access routes, pricing, partnerships, ventures, and next steps through one unified interface.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-card">
                <h3>JayPVentures LLC: Enterprise authority</h3>
                <p>JayPVentures LLC provides infrastructure authority, governance, identity management, security alignment, deployment oversight, and enterprise operations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-card">
                <h3>jaypventures: Creator platform</h3>
                <p>jaypventures is where creators launch products, manage memberships, coordinate community, and build digital ventures through a structured execution framework.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-card">
                <h3>jaypVLabs: Innovation validation</h3>
                <p>jaypVLabs is the validation environment where prototypes, AI behaviors, workflows, and concepts are tested before broader scale deployment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-card">
                <h3>JPV Institute: Knowledge authority</h3>
                <p>JPV Institute provides education, professional development, research coordination, and production knowledge systems for the ecosystem.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
        <SectionHeader Kicker="The Commitment"
                       Title="Operational excellence in everything we do."
                       Description="JPV-OS is built on a commitment to clarity, orchestration, infrastructure integrity, and operational excellence. Every system, route, and pathway is designed to enable people to do their best work." />
        <div class="grid-3">
            <GlassCard Eyebrow="Routing" Title="Infrastructure orchestration" Description="Every path through JPV-OS is a designed journey. Routing is clear, validation is structured, and execution is supported." />
            <GlassCard Eyebrow="Governance" Title="Operational integrity" Description="Governance is built in, not bolted on. Policies, standards, reviews, and authority are embedded into the infrastructure itself." />
            <GlassCard Eyebrow="Partnership" Title="Ecosystem alignment" Description="Partners, ventures, creators, and enterprises all operate within the same framework. Alignment is automatic, coordination is orchestrated." />
        </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection Title="Join the ecosystem."
                Description="Whether you're a creator, partner, enterprise, or innovator, JPV-OS has a path for you."
                PrimaryCta="Get init"
                PrimaryHref="/pricing"
                SecondaryCta="Explore Ecosystem"
                SecondaryHref="/ecosystem" />
</div>
